"Rule&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Pandemic game&lt;/em&gt;"
"&amp;nbsp;so that when the stock quantity drops below 5, Odoo automatically "
"creates&amp;nbsp;a purchase order to replenish the stock to 15 games.\n"
